            "id": 6009064,
            "title": "烏克蘭射飛彈！空襲俄羅斯境內飛彈部隊",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>烏克蘭武裝部隊總參謀部周四（5 日）在社交媒體發文，稱當天上午在國家安全局等多個機關配合下，烏軍對布良斯克州俄羅斯飛彈部隊聚集區發動飛彈襲擊，導致俄羅斯飛彈發射器爆炸。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009064%2Fl%2F02e9a2567839a16566967a24e486b64a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">烏克蘭射飛彈！空襲俄羅斯境內飛彈部隊。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>烏克蘭武裝部隊總參謀部說，位於布良斯克州克林齊的俄軍第 26 火箭旅試圖對烏克蘭境內發動飛彈襲擊，襲擊目標可能是烏克蘭首都基輔市。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>得益於有效偵察和烏軍與烏國家安全局配合，烏軍對該火箭旅的飛彈部隊聚集區發動襲擊，俄軍一個飛彈發射器爆炸，另有多個發射器可能受損。烏方正在核實俄軍損失情況。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據烏媒報導，俄軍第 26 火箭旅擁有「伊斯坎德爾」彈道飛彈，發生爆炸的是「伊斯坎德爾」飛彈發射器。目前俄羅斯尚未對此作出回應。<br/>\n </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
