        {
            "id": 6009217,
            "title": "Uber評估是否導入穩定幣 以降低全球資金轉移成本",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>《彭博》周四 (5 日) 報導，Uber(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UBER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UBER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UBER-US</a>) 執行長克斯洛沙西 (Dara Khosrowshahi) 表示，該公司正考慮使用穩定幣作為全球資金轉移工具，目前處於「研究階段」。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009217%2Fl%2F84d1eb02a68e6511645a5de15fb54bba.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">Uber執行長克斯洛沙西表示正評估穩定幣應用。(圖:Shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>克斯洛沙西周四在舊金山舉行的彭博科技會議上接受訪問時表示，穩定幣 (Stablecoin) 似乎具有「超越<a href=\"https://crypto.cnyes.com/BTC/24h\" target=\"_blank\">加密貨幣</a>歷史價值的實用效益」。他補充說，這項技術「對全球企業而言相當有前景」，因為可以幫助降低不同國家間資金轉移的成本。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>他說：「這對我們來說非常有趣，我們絕對會仔細研究。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>穩定幣是通常與美元或其他貨幣掛鉤、由準備金支持的數位代幣，例如 USDT、USDC、BUSD 等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>穩定幣的潛在優勢包括更快的交易處理時間、較低的手續費，以及減少對傳統銀行系統的依賴。這些特點對需要頻繁進行國際資金調度的跨國企業特別具有吸引力，而 Uber 就在全球 70 多個國家營運。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國國會議員日前已提出立法建議，擬對穩定幣進行監管。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
